<div class="col-sm-8">

<p>
Welcome to the British Institute at Ankara Research Resource Centre.
Here, you can search, browse or find detailed information about the BIAA  <a href="library"><u>David French Library</u></a> and the BIAA <a href="collections">collections and databases. </a>
</p>
<p>
The Research Resource Centre hosts over 65,000 records of books, pamphlets, theses, maps and journals, as well as large collections of squeezes, ceramic sherd assemblages, photographs and slides, bones and specimens.  There are also various thematic bibliographies.   
</p>
<p>
For detailed information about BIAA membership, research activities and grants, please visit the  <a href="http://www.biaa.ac.uk/" target="_blank">BIAA home page</a>. 




 
 
 </div> 
 
